# JWT Setup

Generate a key and paste it into your `.env`:

```bash
python -c "import secrets; print(secrets.token_urlsafe(64))"
```

```env
{{ project_slug | upper }}_JWT_SECRET_KEY=<paste-here>
{{ project_slug | upper }}_JWT_EXPIRE_MINUTES=30
```

Staging/prod require a key of at least 32 characters (app refuses to start otherwise).
Local dev works with the default value.

Tokens are sent as `Authorization: Bearer <token>`. Algorithm: HS256.
